    <p>The new out­lets are at Junc­tion 8 (open), Chi­na­town Point (open­ing on Oct 12), Wisma Atria (open­ing on</p>
    <p>Oct 15) and SingPost Cen­tre (open­ing on Oct 23). To cel­e­brate the open­ings, Yanmi Yo­gurt will of­fer a one-for-one pro­mo­tion for its Pur­ple Rice Yo­gurt ($4.80) for a lim­ited time. Fans can also en­joy of­fer­ings from the In­dul­gence Yo­gurt se­ries, such as Roasted Brown Su­gar Boba Yo­gurt ($4.80) and Ky­oto Matcha Red-bean Yo­gurt ($5.30).</p>
    <p>WHERE: Junc­tion 8: 02-30, 9 Bis­han Place; Chi­na­town Point: B1-38, 133 New Bridge Road; Wisma Atria: B1-44, 435 Or­chard Road; SingPost Cen­tre: B1-149, 10 Eunos Road 8 MRT: Bis­han/ Chi­na­town/Or­chard/Paya Le­bar WHEN: 10.30am - 10pm daily; one-for-one pro­mo­tion – Junc­tion 8: to­day - Sun; Chi­na­town Point: Oct 16 - 18; Wisma Atria: Oct 23 - 25;</p>
    <p>SingPost Cen­tre: Oct 23 - 25</p>
    <p>INFO: www.face­book.com/ yan­miyo­gurt</p>


